# Huong dan Nang cao: Dieu khien Giong noi Bieu cam voi Qwen3-TTS (2025)

Dua tren cac phan tich tu blog chinh thuc cua Qwen (15/01/2025), code thuc te va ket qua Multi-Agent Brainstorming Review.

---

## 1. Kien truc 3 Tang Dieu khien Voice (3-Layer Voice Control)

```
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|                LAYER 1: MODEL SELECTION              |
|  Chon model quyet dinh PHUONG THUC dieu khien        |
|  +-------------- +--------------+----------------+   |
|  | VoiceDesign   | CustomVoice  |    Base         |   |
|  | (1.7B only)   | (0.6B/1.7B)  | (Voice Clone)  |   |
|  +------+--------+------+-------+------+----------+   |
|         |               |              |              |
+---------v---------------v--------------v--------------+
|                LAYER 2: INSTRUCT                      |
|  Dieu khien AM SAC + TRANG THAI tong the              |
|  (AI dang noi giong gi, cam xuc gi)                   |
|                                                       |
+-------------------------------------------------------+
|                LAYER 3: TEXT                           |
|  Dieu khien HANH VI cu the tung khoanh khac           |
|  (cuoi, tho, nghi, thay doi tong)                     |
+-------------------------------------------------------+
```

**Nguyen tac cot loi:**
- **Instruct:** Quyet dinh *Giong ai dang noi* va *Trang thai cam xuc tong the*.
- **Text:** Quyet dinh *Hanh vi cu the tung thoi diem* (cuoi, tho, nghi).

---

## 2. Quick Start - Chon Model nao?

```
Ban co file audio mau?
  |-- CO  --> Dung Base (Voice Clone)
  +-- KHONG --> Ban can giong moi hoan toan?
                 |-- CO  --> Dung VoiceDesign 1.7B
                 +-- KHONG --> Dung CustomVoice (chon 1 trong 9 speaker)
```

### Bang so sanh Model

| Tieu chi | VoiceDesign (1.7B) | CustomVoice (0.6B/1.7B) | Base (Clone) |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Khi nao dung** | Can giong HOAN TOAN MOI tu mo ta | Can giong preset + cam xuc | Can clone giong that |
| **Input** | Full voice description (instruct) | Speaker name + short emotion | Reference audio + text |
| **Do linh hoat** | Cao nhat (mo ta bat ky) | Trung binh (9 preset) | Cao (bat ky giong that) |
| **Tinh nhat quan** | THAP (moi lan generate khac nhau) | CAO (cung speaker = cung giong) | RAT CAO (clone chinh xac) |
| **VRAM** | ~4GB | ~2-4GB | ~4GB |
| **Use case** | YouTube Kids, nhan vat fiction | Audiobook, podcast, da ngon ngu | Dubbing, voice acting |

> **CANH BAO QUAN TRONG:** VoiceDesign tao giong KHAC NHAU moi lan generate. Khong nen dung truc tiep cho content dai nhieu segments. Xem muc "Workflow Production" ben duoi.

---

## 3. LAYER 2: Cach viet Instruct

### RULE #1: Instruct LUON viet bang tieng Anh

Model duoc train tren English instructs. Text (noi dung doc) co the la bat ky ngon ngu nao.

---

### A. VoiceDesign: Full Acoustic Attribute Control

Su dung **7 thuoc tinh** de mo ta giong noi:

| Thuoc tinh | Tu khoa goi y (Tieng Anh) | Y nghia |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Gender** | `Male`, `Female` | Gioi tinh |
| **Age** | `Young adult`, `Middle-aged`, `Teenager`, `Child-like`, `50+`, `60+` | Do tuoi |
| **Pitch** | `Low-pitched`, `High-pitched`, `Stable`, `Very low-pitched` | Cao do |
| **Texture** | `Husky` (khan), `Gravelly` (tram re), `Bright` (sang), `Resonant` (vang), `Breathy` (hoi tho), `Close-mic` (can mic) | Chat giong |
| **Tone** | `Mischievous` (lem linh), `Authoritative` (uy quyen), `Playful` (vui ve), `Menacing` (de doa), `Informal` (than mat), `Warm` (am ap) | Thai do |
| **Emotion** | `Hyper-active` (nang dong), `Panicked` (hoang loan), `Sorrowful` (dau kho), `Excited` (hao hung), `Calm` (binh tinh), `Trembling` (run so) | Cam xuc |
| **Speed** | `Fast-paced`, `Slow and deliberate`, `Moderate pace` | Toc do |

**Vi du Instruct chuan:**

```
# YouTube Kids - nhan vat nu vui ve
"Female young voice. Pitch: high-pitched and clear. Texture: bright. Tone: mischievous, playful, and challenging. Performance: frequent light giggles integrated into the speech. Energy: high."

# Vlogger Reaction (can mic, co hoi tho)
"Male young adult vlogger voice. Texture: breathy, close-mic. Tone: informal and excited."

# Phan dien de doa (CatNap style)
"Male mature. Pitch: very low-pitched. Texture: gravelly with a slight growl. Tone: menacing, authoritative. Speed: slow and deliberate."

# Nhan vat hoang loan (Huggy Wuggy style)
"Male young. Emotion: hyper-active, transitioning from intense anxiety to pouting. Performance: theatrical and exaggerated."

# Narrator truyen kich tinh
"Female 40+. Pitch: stable, warm baritone. Tone: authoritative yet engaging. Speed: moderate."
```

**Bang mapping Tieng Viet --> Instruct:**

| Muon giong | Viet instruct |
|---|---|
| Giong tre con | `Child-like, high-pitched` |
| Giong ong gia | `Male 60+, low-pitched, slow` |
| Giong thi tham | `Whispering, very soft` |
| Giong het | `Shouting, intense, high energy` |
| Giong run so | `Trembling, fearful, shaky` |
| Giong am ap | `Warm, gentle, moderate pace` |
| Giong lanh lung | `Cold, detached, monotone` |
| Giong vui ve | `Cheerful, bright, energetic` |

---

### B. CustomVoice: Speaker Preset + Short Emotion

**9 Speaker co san:**

| Speaker | Mo ta |
|---|---|
| `Ryan` | Giong nam truong thanh, am ap |
| `Vivian` | Giong nu tre trung, trong treo |
| `Serena` | Giong nu am ap, truong thanh |
| `Aiden` | Giong nam tre, nang dong |
| `uncle_fu` | Giong nam lon tuoi |
| `ono_anna` | Giong Nhat nu |
| `sohee` | Giong Han nu |

**Instruct cho CustomVoice = CHI emotion ngan (<50 ky tu):**

```python
# DUNG - Ngan gon, chi mo ta cam xuc
instruct = "Very happy"
instruct = "sad and tearful"
instruct = "Speaking at an extremely slow pace"
instruct = "Shouting angrily"
instruct = "Whispering softly"

# SAI - Dung dung full description cho CustomVoice!
instruct = "Male young adult voice. Pitch: high. Texture: bright..."  # SAI!
```

> **LUU Y:** Model 0.6B **KHONG ho tro instruct** -- chi co speaker name co tac dung. Chi model 1.7B CustomVoice moi nhan instruct.

**Tu dong extract emotion tu full instruct:**

Code `TTSEngine._extract_emotion_modifier()` se tu dong rut gon:
- `"Full description. Emotion: very excited"` --> `"very excited"`
- Instruct ngan < 50 ky tu --> giu nguyen
- Khong match --> fallback `"natural and clear"`

Khuyen dung: Viet instruct ngan tu dau thay vi dua vao auto-extract.

---

### C. Base (Voice Clone): Khong co instruct

Voice Clone dung **reference audio** thay vi instruct:

```python
# Cach 1: Truc tiep tu file audio
wavs, sr = engine._generate_voice_clone(
    texts=["Xin chao!"],
    languages=["auto"],
    ref_audio_path="reference.wav",
    ref_text="Day la giong mau de clone."  # Optional nhung cai thien chat luong
)

# Cach 2: Tao prompt 1 lan, dung lai nhieu lan (KHUYEN DUNG)
prompt = engine.create_voice_clone_prompt("reference.wav", "Transcript cua audio mau")
wavs, sr = engine._generate_voice_clone(
    texts=["Xin chao!", "Hom nay troi dep qua!"],
    languages=["auto", "auto"],
    voice_clone_prompt=prompt
)
```

**2 che do clone:**
- **Full mode** (co ref_text): Clone ca am sac + ngu dieu. Chat luong tot nhat.
- **X-vector only** (khong co ref_text): Chi clone am sac. Nhanh hon, chat luong thap hon.

---

## 4. LAYER 3: Dieu khien hanh vi truc tiep trong Text

**LUU Y CUC KY QUAN TRONG:** Dung bao gio viet ghi chu trong ngoac nhu `(cuoi)` vi AI se doc ca chu do. Hay dung **Tu tuong thanh** va **Ky hieu dac biet**.

### A. Khoang nghi va Ngat quang

| Ky hieu | Hieu ung | Vi du |
|---|---|---|
| `......` | Khoang nghi dai (cang nhieu dau cham nghi cang lau) | `"Doi da...... ok tiep nhe"` |
| `...` | Khoang nghi vua | `"Hmm... thu vi day"` |
| `,` | Khoang nghi ngan | `"Vang, toi hieu roi"` |
| `----` | Ngat quang dot ngot / chuyen tong | `"Dung hong---- roi khoi day"` |

### B. Tieng tho va Bieu cam (Onomatopoeia)

| Tu khoa | Hieu ung | Vi du |
|---|---|---|
| `huh... ha` | Tieng hit tho sau, tho doc | `"huh... ha...... Ok bat dau nhe!"` |
| `--uh--` | Tieng ngap ngung (o, um) | `"Toi --uh-- khong chac lam"` |
| `heh--` | Tieng cuoi khi, lem linh | `"heh-- heh-- heh--! Do bat duoc!"` |
| `huc huc--` | Tieng nac hoac khoc nhe | `"Huc huc-- Dau qua di a......"` |
| `Rum----` | Tieng gam gru, giong quai vat | `"Rum---- Cac nguoi nghi..."` |
| `A!` / `Oi!` | Than tu --> tong cao hoang loan | `"A! Khong khong khong!"` |

### C. Meo nang cao

```python
# 1. GAP DOI tu tuong thanh de keo dai hieu ung
text = "heh-- heh-- heh--! Vui qua di!"       # Trang cuoi dai
text = "huc huc-- huc huc-- Sao lai the..."   # Khoc keo dai

# 2. KET HOP dau cau cho nhip tu nhien
text = "Hmm, thu vi day... de toi nghi da...... Ok! Co roi!"
#       ^ngan    ^vua                    ^dai     ^dot ngot

# 3. CHUYEN TONG bang ----
text = "Toi rat vui---- nhung ma---- that ra cung hoi buon."
```

> **LUU Y:** Onomatopoeia hoat dong ~80% thoi gian. Ket qua co the khac nhau giua cac lan generate. Gap doi/gap ba tu tuong thanh se tang xac suat thanh cong.

---

## 5. Ap dung cho cac mau nhan vat pho bien

### Mau 1: Video Reaction (Can mic, co tieng tho)
- **Model:** VoiceDesign 1.7B
- **Instruct:** `Male young adult vlogger voice. Texture: breathy, close-mic. Tone: informal and excited.`
- **Text:** `huh... ha...... Ok, he lo ca nha nhe! Chao mung moi nguoi da quay tro lai...`

### Mau 2: Nhan vat Nang dong (Huggy Wuggy style)
- **Model:** VoiceDesign 1.7B
- **Instruct:** `Male young. Emotion: hyper-active, transitioning from intense anxiety to pouting. Performance: theatrical and exaggerated.`
- **Text:** `A! Khong khong khong! Chan cua toi dau roi? ...... Huc huc-- Dau qua di a......`

### Mau 3: Nhan vat Phan dien (CatNap style)
- **Model:** VoiceDesign 1.7B
- **Instruct:** `Male mature. Pitch: very low-pitched. Texture: gravelly with a slight growl. Speed: slow and deliberate.`
- **Text:** `Rum---- Cac nguoi nghi minh co the chay thoat sao? ...... Dung hong---- roi khoi day.`

### Mau 4: Audiobook da nhan vat
- **Model:** CustomVoice 1.7B
- **Speaker:** `Serena` (narrator), `Ryan` (nam chinh), `Vivian` (nu chinh)
- **Instruct Narrator:** `Calm, engaging storytelling voice`
- **Instruct Dialog:** Thay doi theo cam xuc: `"angry"`, `"whispering nervously"`, `"laughing happily"`

### Mau 5: Clone giong YouTuber co san
- **Model:** Base (Voice Clone)
- **Input:** File audio mau 3-10 giay + transcript
- **Luu y:** Dung `create_voice_clone_prompt()` 1 lan, tai su dung cho tat ca segments

---

## 6. Workflow Production: Dam bao Nhat quan Giong noi

### Van de: VoiceDesign tao giong khac nhau moi lan

Neu dung VoiceDesign truc tiep cho 50 segments --> 50 giong khac nhau!

### Giai phap A: VoiceDesign + Clone (Khuyen dung)

```python
from gui.core.tts_engine import TTSEngine

# Buoc 1: Tao 1 audio mau bang VoiceDesign
engine_vd = TTSEngine("./Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-VoiceDesign")
engine_vd.load_model()

segments_sample = [{"text": "Day la giong mau.", "instruct": "Female young, bright, playful."}]
gen_time, duration, wavs, sr = engine_vd.generate(
    segments=segments_sample, output_path="voice_sample.wav", batch_size=1
)
engine_vd.unload_model()  # Giai phong VRAM

# Buoc 2: Chuyen sang Base model, tao clone prompt
engine_clone = TTSEngine("./Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-Base")
engine_clone.load_model()

prompt = engine_clone.create_voice_clone_prompt("voice_sample.wav", "Day la giong mau.")

# Buoc 3: Dung prompt cho TAT CA segments (consistency 100%)
segments_full = [
    {"text": "Cau 1 cua truyen..."},
    {"text": "Cau 2 cua truyen..."},
    {"text": "Cau 3 cua truyen..."},
]
gen_time, duration, wavs, sr = engine_clone.generate(
    segments=segments_full, output_path="output_full.wav",
    batch_size=16, voice_clone_prompt=prompt
)
```

### Giai phap B: Dung CustomVoice (Don gian hon)

```python
engine = TTSEngine("./Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice")
engine.load_model()

# Cung speaker = cung giong, chi thay doi emotion
segments = [
    {"text": "Cau 1...", "instruct": "calm narration", "speaker": "Serena"},
    {"text": "Cau 2...", "instruct": "excited", "speaker": "Serena"},
    {"text": "Cau 3...", "instruct": "sad and tearful", "speaker": "Serena"},
]
gen_time, duration, wavs, sr = engine.generate(
    segments=segments, output_path="output.wav", batch_size=16, speaker="Serena"
)
```

---

## 7. Toi uu hoa trong Code Python

### Gioi han Segment

- Moi segment toi da **~50-80 tu** (~15-17 giay audio)
- `max_new_tokens=2048` gioi han do dai audio output
- Text dai hon se bi cat ma khong co warning
- Luon chia nho text thanh segments truoc khi generate

### Code mau an toan

```python
from gui.core.tts_engine import TTSEngine

# Khoi tao
engine = TTSEngine("./Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-VoiceDesign")
engine.load_model()

# Cau truc Segment chuan
segments = [
    {
        "text": "huh... ha...... He lo ca nha!",
        "instruct": "Male vlogger voice, breathy, excited."
    }
]

# Goi ham tao an toan (da co torch.no_grad() ben trong)
gen_time, duration, wavs, sr = engine.generate(
    segments=segments,
    output_path="output.wav",
    batch_size=1
)
```

> **TIP:** Luon su dung `engine.generate()` thay vi goi cac ham noi bo (`_generate_voice_design`, v.v.) de dam bao GPU duoc giai phong bo nho sau moi lan tao.

### Su dung AI (Gemini) phan tich tu dong

Xem file `test_story_roleplay2.py` de tham khao cach:
1. Dung Gemini phan tich truyen --> nhan dien nhan vat
2. Tu dong gan speaker + emotion instruct cho tung doan thoai
3. Batch generate theo speaker group de toi uu toc do

---

## 8. Meo nho de giong that hon

1. **Gap doi tu tuong thanh:** Thay vi `heh--`, hay dung `heh-- heh-- heh--` de tao trang cuoi dai.
2. **Ket hop dau cham va dau phay:** Dau phay tao khoang nghi ngan, dau cham tao khoang nghi vua, va `......` tao khoang nghi dai.
3. **Tan dung VoiceDesign + Clone:** Tao giong doc ban bang VoiceDesign, sau do Clone de giu tinh on dinh.
4. **Test nhanh voi Gradio:** Dung `python app_local.py` de thu giong interactive truoc khi viet code.
5. **CustomVoice cho production:** 9 speaker preset du cho hau het use cases va dam bao consistency.

---

## 9. Bang tom tat Compatibility

| Tinh nang | VoiceDesign 1.7B | CustomVoice 1.7B | CustomVoice 0.6B | Base 1.7B | Base 0.6B |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Full instruct (7 thuoc tinh) | CO | KHONG | KHONG | KHONG | KHONG |
| Short emotion instruct | KHONG (dung full) | CO | KHONG | KHONG | KHONG |
| Speaker preset | KHONG | CO (9 speakers) | CO (9 speakers) | KHONG | KHONG |
| Voice clone tu audio | KHONG | KHONG | KHONG | CO | CO |
| Onomatopoeia trong text | CO | CO | CO | CO | CO |
| Consistency giua segments | THAP | CAO | CAO | RAT CAO | RAT CAO |
| VRAM can thiet | ~4GB | ~4GB | ~2GB | ~4GB | ~2GB |

---

## 10. Troubleshooting

| Van de | Nguyen nhan | Giai phap |
|---|---|---|
| Giong khac nhau moi lan | Dung VoiceDesign truc tiep | Chuyen sang Clone workflow hoac CustomVoice |
| AI doc chu `(cuoi)` thay vi cuoi | Viet ghi chu trong ngoac | Dung onomatopoeia: `heh--` |
| Instruct khong co tac dung | Dung model 0.6B hoac viet qua dai | Kiem tra model version, viet ngan < 50 chars |
| Audio bi cat ngang | Segment qua dai | Chia nho text, moi segment < 80 tu |
| Giong khong giong audio mau | Khong co ref_text | Them transcript cua audio mau de tang chat luong |
| OOM (het VRAM) | Batch size qua lon | Giam batch_size xuong 1-4, goi `torch.cuda.empty_cache()` |
